title: Refrigerator Evaporator/Condensor Fan Grommet
description: Refrigerator Evaporator/Condensor Fan Grommet ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 12 Reviews PartSelect Number PS284555 Manufacturer Part Number WR02X10098 This evaporator fan motor grommet, or condenser fan grommet is built for refrigerators. It provides a cushion between the fan motor and the motor mounting bracket. It is made or round, black plastic and is approximately one inch in diameter. If your grommet is torn or damaged and you are getting noise from the fan motor, you may need to replace it. This is an OEM part sourced directly from the manufacturer.

The repair was with no difficulty,and time spend around 20 min. Thanks.PartSelect,your delivery and easy way to place an order is great. Thanks. Joel
